{
  "id": "RAW_196a4a11",
  "title": "Dexmal 原力灵机提出 GeoVLA，打破 2D 视觉枷锁，让机器人看懂三维世界",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwNzc2NTk0NQ==&mid=2247613942&idx=2&sn=17fc20d39a711cc8b2110d68b9f0bc16",
  "date": "2025-12-25 07:51:00",
  "author": "夕小瑶科技说",
  "siteName": "夕小瑶科技说",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">在具身智能的浪潮中，VLA 模型被视为通往通用机器人的快车道。然而，随着研究深入到非结构化环境，现有 VLA 模型面临着一个严重的维度缺陷：空间失明。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，大多数 VLA 模型（比如 OpenVLA、RT-2、Pi0、Pi05）单纯依赖 2D RGB 图像作为视觉输入，导致模型眼中的世界“纸片化”，严重缺乏深度信息和几何先验；由此带来的后果是：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 25px;padding-right: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);margin-left: 10px;margin-top: 22px;margin-right: 10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">深度感知缺失：面对需要精确距离判断的任务，比如精准投篮、挂扣环，2D 模型往往“抓瞎”，无法准确预测 Z 轴的动作。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间适应性差：一旦物体尺寸发生变化（Scale Variance）或相机视角发生偏移（Viewpoint Shift），便无法理解物体在空间中的本质位置，导致任务失败。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图 1：GeoVLA 整体示意图\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100130273\" data-ratio=\"0.3592592592592593\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: none;width: 100%;border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 0px;border-top-width: initial;border-right-width: initial;border-bottom-width: initial;border-left-width: initial;border-top-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: initial;border-left-color: initial;border-image-source: initial;border-image-slice: initial;border-image-width: initial;border-image-outset: initial;border-image-repeat: initial;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c0ae6c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5fknb41ib9qH96EcJQfMSTlLLtDibJI6vSOCSWsDY63um9yDVzfF9Tnv77V1SMAaFfTrVssxRPTo3dzC5dLnaSYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: center;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 0px;background-size: 11px 11px;width: 100%;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">图 1：GeoVLA 整体示意图</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">Dexmal 原力灵机作者团队提出一种全新的 VLA 框架 GeoVLA，它在保留现有视觉-语言模型（VLM）的预训练能力的同时，采用了一种优雅的双流架构（Dual-path Architecture）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100130287\" data-ratio=\"0.4064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3a6e6ba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5fknb41ib9qH96EcJQfMSTlLLtDibJI6vSLLFtTeib8SBDsMhJV4LmcQjSpHsQZAIKk7nyya9M4duMQ3HMAes8eicw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:16px;border-left-color:rgb(192, 178, 190);margin-left:12px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:dashed;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;overflow-x:auto;margin-top:20px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;overflow-y:auto;background-image:none;height:auto;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;padding-top:0px;border-right-width:3px;display:block;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;line-height:10px;border-left-width:1px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;border-bottom-width:3px;width:auto;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:20px;padding-right:16px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(143, 137, 143);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 6px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 6px;margin-left: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名称：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(143, 137, 143);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 6px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 6px;margin-left: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">GeoVLA: Empowering 3D Representation in Vision-Language-Action Models</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><span leaf=\"\">论文链接：&nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(143, 137, 143);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 6px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 6px;margin-left: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2508.09071v2\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/html/2508.09071v2</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><span leaf=\"\">项目主页：&nbsp;</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(143, 137, 143);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 6px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 6px;margin-left: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://linsun449.github.io/GeoVLA/\" target=\"_blank\">https://linsun449.github.io/GeoVLA/</a></span></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体而言，GeoVLA 在保留 VLM 强大的语义理解能力的同时，引入专用的点云嵌入网络 PEN 和空间感知动作专家 3DAE，直接利用深度图生成的点云数据，赋予机器人真正的三维几何感知能力。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一设计不仅在仿真环境中取得 SOTA，更在真实世界的鲁棒性测试中，特别是在视角改变和物体尺度变化的极端条件下，展现出惊人的适应力。</span></p>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;text-align: left;margin-top: 50px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);line-height: 35px;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;display: block;padding-left: 10px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);\"><span leaf=\"\">方法框架</span></strong></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">常见的做法试图让一个 VLM 既懂语义又懂几何，这往往顾此失彼；GeoVLA 的核心逻辑是选择把任务解耦：让 VLM 负责“看懂是什么”，让点云网络负责“看清在哪里”。</span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100130274\" data-ratio=\"0.3425925925925926\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: none;width: 100%;border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 0px;border-top-width: initial;border-right-width: initial;border-bottom-width: initial;border-left-width: initial;border-top-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: initial;border-left-color: initial;border-image-source: initial;border-image-slice: initial;border-image-width: initial;border-image-outset: initial;border-image-repeat: initial;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a1f0d2a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5fknb41ib9qH96EcJQfMSTlLLtDibJI6vSG9m2icgae3xY0TuRgDowEtI6zXqH8ASTYjeKaWiaDHEsJcribZKj1ib4mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: center;font-weight: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;background-size: 11px 11px;width: 100%;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 20px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">图 2：GeoVLA 框架图</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">GeoVLA 是一个全新的端到端框架，其流程包含三个关键组件的协同工作：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 25px;padding-right: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);margin-left: 10px;margin-top: 22px;margin-right: 10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">语义理解流：利用预训练的 VLM（如 Prismatic-7B）处理 RGB 图像和语言指令，提取融合后的视觉-语言特征。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">几何感知流：利用点云嵌入网络 PEN 处理由深度图转换而来的点云，独立提取高精度的 3D 几何特征。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">动作生成流：通过 3D 增强动作专家 3DAE 融合上述两种特征，生成精确的动作序列。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;text-align: left;margin-top: 50px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);line-height: 30px;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: 500;display: block;padding-left: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">点云嵌入网络 PEN&nbsp;</span></span></h3>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图 3：双路径点云嵌入网络细节图\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100130272\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: none;width: 100%;border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 0px;border-top-width: initial;border-right-width: initial;border-bottom-width: initial;border-left-width: initial;border-top-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: initial;border-left-color: initial;border-image-source: initial;border-image-slice: initial;border-image-width: initial;border-image-outset: initial;border-image-repeat: initial;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dfa3174c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5fknb41ib9qH96EcJQfMSTlLLtDibJI6vSsrKlQpAwbHdY2Wicqr3lLwyIUZma5KwtqQBmMcIibScmW6ZXdClQpf1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: center;font-weight: normal;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 0px;background-size: 11px 11px;width: 100%;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">图 3：双路径点云嵌入网络细节图</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">原始深度图往往包含大量噪声，且数据稀疏，直接作为输入效果不佳。点云嵌入网络 PEN 专为机器人操作设计，采用双路径架构来提取干净且紧凑的几何特征：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 25px;padding-right: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);margin-left: 10px;margin-top: 22px;margin-right: 10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">几何特征提取：使用大核卷积和局部池化的轻量级 CNN，将非结构化的点云编码为 Patch 级别的几何 Token。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间位置编码：引入在大语言模型中常见的旋转位置编码 RoPE，它能极好地保留 3D 空间中的相对位置信息，这对于操作任务至关重要。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间锚点（Spatial Anchor）设计是 PEN 的一大亮点。作者团队并没有简单地对所有点云特征进行平均池化，而是选择对应于末端执行器坐标原点的 Token 作为“锚点”。这种以“手”为中心的视角设计，让模型能够显式地建模“手”与“物体”之间的几何关系，大幅提升操作精度。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;text-align: left;margin-top: 50px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);line-height: 30px;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: 500;display: block;padding-left: 10px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);\"><span leaf=\"\">3D 增强动作专家 3DAE</span></strong></span></h3>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">特征提取只是第一步，如何有效融合 RGB 的语义信息和点云的几何信息，实现 1+1＞2 的效果，是多模态研究当中的难点。作者团队在动作生成端采用基于扩散 Transformer (DiTs) 的架构，并创新性地引入混合专家 (MoE) 机制。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 25px;padding-right: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);margin-left: 10px;margin-top: 22px;margin-right: 10px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">静态路由策略 (Static Routing)：这是一个直觉且有效的策略。在训练过程中，由于 VLM 分支是预训练的，而点云分支是从头开始学，如果使用常规的动态路由，模型会倾向于走捷径，只依赖 VLM 分支，忽略点云信息。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">强制解耦：作者团队采用了静态路由，随机丢弃某种模态，逼迫模型必须学会独立利用几何信息来解决问题，从而确保了双流信息的有效融合。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;display: flex;text-align: left;margin-top: 50px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);line-height: 35px;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: 400;display: block;padding-left: 10px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-top-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-width: 3px;border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius: 0px;border-top-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;color: rgb(146, 59, 208);\"><span leaf=\"\">实验结果</span></strong></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80);font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 0.2px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 12px;margin-bottom: 12px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 12px;font-weight: 400;\"><span leaf=\"\">GeoVLA 在仿真和真机实验中均展现出对传统 2D VLA 模型的压倒性优势，证明显式 3D 表征在复杂操作中的不可替代性。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bott